# Sub-Task 4.1: Langflow Version Control Setup

## OBJECTIVE
Establish Git as single source of truth for all Langflow flow definitions.
Every flow deployed to Langflow MUST have a corresponding versioned JSON in Git.

## FLOW METADATA SCHEMA
Every `flows/definitions/{domain}/metadata.yaml` MUST follow this schema:

```yaml
flows:
  fhir-validator-v1:
    flowId: "flow-fhir-v1"
    domain: "healthcare"           # healthcare | academic | orchestrator
    version: "1.0.0"
    owner: "healthcare-team"
    description: "Validates FHIR Patient resources against R4 profiles"
    status: "production"           # draft | staging | production | rollback
    testCoverage: 0.95
    expectedLatency: "2000ms"
    costPerRun: "$0.025"
    dependencies:
      - "@the-abyss/fhir-engine"
      - "@the-abyss/ai-core"
    shadowMode:
      enabled: true
      shadowFlowId: "flow-fhir-v2"
      minAgreementRate: 0.90
```

## SYNC FLOWS CLI — `flows/scripts/sync-flows.ts`

```typescript
import { LangflowClient } from '@the-abyss/langflow-client';
import * as fs from 'fs';

async function syncFlows() {
  const client = new LangflowClient({
    baseUrl: process.env.LANGFLOW_API_URL,
    apiKey: process.env.LANGFLOW_API_KEY,
  });

  const flows = await client.listFlows();
  for (const flow of flows) {
    const definition = await client.exportFlow(flow.id);
    const filePath = `flows/definitions/${flow.domain}/${flow.name}-v${flow.version}.json`;
    fs.writeFileSync(filePath, JSON.stringify(definition, null, 2));
    console.log(`✅ Exported: ${filePath}`);
  }
}

syncFlows();
```

## GIT HOOKS CONFIGURATION

```bash
# .husky/pre-commit
pnpm abyss validate-flows        # Validate JSON schema
jq empty flows/definitions/**/*.json  # JSON syntax check

# .husky/pre-push
pnpm abyss validate-flows        # Component compatibility check

# .husky/post-merge
pnpm abyss sync-flows --target staging  # Auto-sync to staging
```

## GITHUB ACTIONS — `sync-flows.yml`

```yaml
name: Sync Langflow Definitions
on:
  schedule:
    - cron: '0 */6 * * *'  # Every 6 hours
  workflow_dispatch:
jobs:
  sync:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - name: Sync Flows from Langflow
        run: pnpm abyss sync-flows
      - name: Validate Flow Definitions
        run: pnpm abyss validate-flows
      - name: Commit Changes
        run: |
          git config user.name "Langflow Bot"
          git add flows/definitions/
          git diff --staged --quiet || git commit -m "chore: sync flows from Langflow"
          git push
```

